trans-unit.source: Annotations are `strings` that you define that contain information to associate with certain kinds of tracking data.
trans-unit.target: As anotações são `strings` definir que contêm informações para associar a determinados tipos de dados de rastreamento.

Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> class by using a list of string annotations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> usando uma lista de anotações de cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection> is initialized to contain the strings specified in `annotations`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection> é inicializada para conter as cadeias de caracteres especificadas em `annotations`.
